Compile the Project
If you want to create a standalone executable, you can compile the project using PyInstaller or Nuitka.

Using PyInstaller:

 
 
pyinstaller --additional-hooks-dir=. -F --onefile laZagne.py
Using Nuitka:

 
 
python3 -m nuitka --standalone --onefile --include-package=lazagne laZagne.py
